short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Zombie Shooter is shooting game where you free the city from hordes of zombies. Now you can play on Chrome browser!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_GB,es,e: Zombie Shooter is an extension version on Chrome Browser, providing players with an exciting and scary shooting game. In this game, players must face a horde of attacking zombies and shoot them to survive. Players will have a variety of weapons to choose from and must use them wisely to defeat the zombies. With beautiful graphics and an engaging gaming experience, the Zombie Shooter extension version on Chrome Browser is an excellent choice for entertainment and challenging your shooting skills.

Zombie Shooter is an extension version on Chrome Browser, providing players with an exciting and scary shooting game. With beautiful graphics and an engaging gaming experience, the Zombie Shooter extension version on Chrome Browser is an excellent choice for entertainment and challenging your shooting skills.
